name: memory_profiler
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.41" %}

package:
  name: memory_profiler
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: memory_profiler-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/m/memory_profiler/memory_profiler-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 8615aecbcc5cf1a761c819b9f4976cad

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python

  run:
    - python
    - psutil

test:
  imports:
    - memory_profiler

  commands:
    - python -m memory_profiler --help

about:
  home: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/memory_profiler
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: A module for monitoring memory usage of a python program

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham

about.summary: A module for monitoring memory usage of a python program
